  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dba \u0dc0\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd1\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The all-electric plane is becoming a reality",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The world's first all-electric passenger plane is about to take off. The Alice plane, made by Israeli company Aviation, underwent an engine check last week at Arlington Municipal Airport, north of Seattle.",
        "Designed with battery technology similar to that of an electric car or mobile phone, this aircraft is capable of traveling for an hour with a 30-minute charge.",
        "The nine-passenger Alice can fly about 440 nautical miles in an hour. The maximum cruising speed of the plane is 287 miles per hour. The company, which focuses exclusively on electric flights, expects to make electric planes that can carry 20 to 40 passengers a reality within seven to 10 years.",
        "The company has developed three versions of the prototype: a \"passenger\" variant, an executive version and a cargo-specific one. The passenger plane configuration can carry nine passengers and two pilots as well as 850 pounds of cargo. The executive design has six passenger seats for a more spacious flight, and the cargo plane holds 450 cubic feet of volume.",
        "All this can be done while reducing the maintenance and operating costs of commercial jets by up to 70%, according to the company."
      ],
